## In just a sentence or two, summarize your project. (E.g., "A website that lets you buy and sell stocks.")

A website that will have a character uploaded with the intention of dodging objects as they float around. 

## In a paragraph or more, detail your project. What will your software do? What features will it have? How will it be executed?

Our software will be an interactive game where a snake moves freely across the screen and dodgers any stuff. The player’s goal is to control the snake to dodge
any obstacle, if it does it hit an obstacle or the wall, the game will end. This game is mainl about survival and using the player’s reflexes. Some key 
features that we will be using are, free flowing snake movement, obstacle generation, collision detection, keyboard input, score/time tracker, and a restart option.  
Our software will be able to start the game at the psuh of a button and 

